        "timestamp": "2022-01-27 19:19:03.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 6:\n\nThanks Lukasz for your valuable feedback.\n1. Code has been refactored to add a new method to reduce duplicate code.\n\n2. Vnf lookup from vf-module has been enhanced. We added another check of modelcustomizationid to the filter. Based on the testing, we don't allow same vf-module instanceNames for same modelcustomizationid in the request.\n\n3. As for as the comment related to network is concerned - we did not want to change the code behaviour for this use case and thus kept it this way. If we are adding the suggested check then we are changing the code behaviour.",
